  "3262520": {
    "name": "Victory of Seeker",
    "steam_appid": 3262520,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们生活在一个充满压力的世界，这就是为什么我们需要创建这个游戏项目。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262520/extras/33d145598da8987a0c938208c40c4154.poster.avif?t=1745380413\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262520/extras/33d145598da8987a0c938208c40c4154.webm?t=1745380413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262520/extras/33d145598da8987a0c938208c40c4154.mp4?t=1745380413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262520/extras/28649abea892a91aaea3070dedec867d.poster.avif?t=1745380413\" width=512 height=512 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262520/extras/28649abea892a91aaea3070dedec867d.webm?t=1745380413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262520/extras/e1949fe462480598f5dfcdef01ea8a79.avif?t=1745380413\" width=800 height=446 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所以在大多数游戏中，英雄是有能力、坚强、挺身而出拯救世界免遭邪恶的人，对吧？但这款游戏不同。失败者或傻瓜也可以成为英雄！所以我们收集了几个失败者的角色作为游戏的主角。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您将成为最终的经理，决定可爱的傻瓜的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有时经理必须在迷你游戏中与其他经理战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262520/extras/93c10318536652173da14967429b62ad.avif?t=1745380413\" width=622 height=334 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以使用以下傻瓜的例子：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了拉屎什么都不会做的小孩。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个漂亮女孩，心态不切实际地积极，她的个人资料照片甚至与现实相去甚远。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个在聊天室里到处撒谎的网络喷子。想象一下，如果你能成为一个用键盘作为武器打人然后逃跑的喷子，那该有多有趣。但他们跑得很快。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个失业的自由艺术家，他的主要技能是当乞丐。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还有更多。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个傻瓜都有自己独特的技能，比如偷钱、设陷阱、用脏话攻击，甚至对对手放屁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Main Game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一般的MOBA游戏中，我们会让英雄比对方更强大，入侵并摧毁敌人的堡垒。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但是!!!这个游戏显然不同，作为一个聪明的人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你和你的伙伴必须计算和计划，通过尽一切可能，攻击敌人，抢劫，建造建筑物以获取利益，并制定防御策略，让你的团队在给定的时间内最富有。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏规则</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 选择你最喜欢的 Sucker</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 使用你的 Sucker 建造建筑物来赚取收入</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 带上 Sucker 到建筑物中训练以加强建筑物</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 从建筑物中收集钱财，随身携带或存放在主楼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >因为总分只会计算从主楼和 Sucker 那里收集的钱财</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 在时间耗尽之前，Billy 会出现。如果任何 Sucker 杀死它，Sucker 身上的钱财将乘以 2</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 时间耗尽时，拥有最多钱财的队伍将获胜</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Lots of features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262520/extras/4ee165eee62050254e3ec8663fd08b56.avif?t=1745380413\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262520/extras_big/4ee165eee62050254e3ec8663fd08b56.avif?t=1745380413 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262520/extras/426c1d78d9913403a33b629867c15b46.avif?t=1745380413\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262520/extras_big/426c1d78d9913403a33b629867c15b46.avif?t=1745380413 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262520/extras/199f5ddd305c086737fea369a47007d8.avif?t=1745380413\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262520/extras_big/199f5ddd305c086737fea369a47007d8.avif?t=1745380413 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262520/extras/53fb0be19db8e2cb4956fbd120b79b28.avif?t=1745380413\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262520/extras_big/53fb0be19db8e2cb4956fbd120b79b28.avif?t=1745380413 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262520/extras/d25661f8fa127ebc337b9dfd984b459e.avif?t=1745380413\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262520/extras_big/d25661f8fa127ebc337b9dfd984b459e.avif?t=1745380413 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262520/extras/9cbd06b32dadbe0f96facd22c79a8906.avif?t=1745380413\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262520/extras_big/9cbd06b32dadbe0f96facd22c79a8906.avif?t=1745380413 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262520/extras/8c5d44c32def0028e1e6a718fe998d7b.avif?t=1745380413\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262520/extras_big/8c5d44c32def0028e1e6a718fe998d7b.avif?t=1745380413 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262520/extras/bb1c418831db0f436820c9571958ffda.avif?t=1745380413\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262520/extras_big/bb1c418831db0f436820c9571958ffda.avif?t=1745380413 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262520/extras/efb6d698c13f06457a729b0c4eee9d4d.avif?t=1745380413\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262520/extras_big/efb6d698c13f06457a729b0c4eee9d4d.avif?t=1745380413 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262520/extras/29914f2cb1dc00d73a6964e5bc1f9d06.avif?t=1745380413\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262520/extras_big/29914f2cb1dc00d73a6964e5bc1f9d06.avif?t=1745380413 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262520/extras/6ecb69443eb2158239df87c64ed53226.avif?t=1745380413\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262520/extras_big/6ecb69443eb2158239df87c64ed53226.avif?t=1745380413 width=1170 height=658 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262520/extras/2b4c696cb86a0fbbbae9db36b35cf13b.avif?t=1745380413\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262520/extras_big/2b4c696cb86a0fbbbae9db36b35cf13b.avif?t=1745380413 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragrap